# `libsagui-docker`

Official Docker image for Sagui library.

# Building latest version

```bash
./make.sh
```

# Generated files

```bash
$ tree -L 1 output/
output/
├── html
├── libsagui-2.5.3_checksums.txt
├── libsagui-2.5.3-linux_amd64.tar.gz
├── libsagui-2.5.3-windows_386.zip
└── libsagui-2.5.3-windows_amd64.zip

1 directory, 4 files
```
